1
00:00:12,380 --> 00:00:18,540
♪My heart flipped when a dynamic
flashed between us someday♪

2
00:00:19,020 --> 00:00:20,380
♪Guided by instinct♪

3
00:00:20,540 --> 00:00:24,660
♪We feel the same reason,
harboring a special feeling underneath♪

4
00:00:24,860 --> 00:00:27,780
♪Amidst the ecstatic shock♪

5
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:30,900
♪I begin to doubt what I see♪

6
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:36,380
♪I can't believe you made me compromise♪

7
00:00:37,060 --> 00:00:40,100
♪The world you're sick of♪

8
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:43,060
♪I look into it thoroughly♪

9
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:45,340
♪How lucky I am to console you♪

10
00:00:45,540 --> 00:00:48,940
♪When you suffer alone♪

11
00:00:49,180 --> 00:00:54,940
♪Yet I realize♪

12
00:00:55,180 --> 00:01:00,100
♪I cannot let go
of the love I hold onto tightly♪

13
00:01:00,300 --> 00:01:03,300
♪As I venture into the world
from a mundane life♪

14
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:06,980
♪You show up at the exact moment♪

15
00:01:07,260 --> 00:01:09,740
♪My ambition♪

16
00:01:09,900 --> 00:01:12,420
♪Puts an end to this aimless journey♪

17
00:01:12,620 --> 00:01:15,580
♪The familiar light of pursuit
shines into my heart♪

18
00:01:15,820 --> 00:01:18,660
♪From the starting point♪

19
00:01:36,420 --> 00:01:41,380
[South Wind Knows]

20
00:01:41,380 --> 00:01:45,380
[Episode 16]

21
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:08,490
[Sun Cheng]

22
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:24,060
[Sun Cheng]
Go on.

23
00:02:24,980 --> 00:02:25,500
Mr. Fu.

24
00:02:26,180 --> 00:02:27,140
Guess what?

25
00:02:27,460 --> 00:02:28,900
Your brother came out.

26
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:31,100
Can you believe this?

27
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:33,860
Why?

28
00:02:34,060 --> 00:02:35,620
Because of that female doctor.

29
00:02:37,620 --> 00:02:38,540
Keep monitoring him.

30
00:02:39,420 --> 00:02:39,980
All right.

31
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:32,980
Zhizhi, I'm here.

32
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:40,820
Your wedding present.

33
00:03:41,420 --> 00:03:42,140
Thank you.

34
00:03:44,540 --> 00:03:45,780
What has happened to you?

35
00:03:46,060 --> 00:03:47,140
You wouldn't tell on the phone.

36
00:03:47,180 --> 00:03:48,060
I'm so worried about you.

37
00:03:50,020 --> 00:03:51,140
I saw her.

38
00:03:52,380 --> 00:03:53,220
Who is it?

39
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:54,580
Zhu Jiu.

40
00:03:55,180 --> 00:03:56,380
The girl Yunshen likes.

41
00:03:57,860 --> 00:03:58,780
Zhu Jiu?

42
00:03:59,620 --> 00:04:01,500
Are you talking about Dr. Zhu?

43
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,380
Do you know her?

44
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:06,100
I do.

45
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:08,980
We met when we were in Country M.

46
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:09,940
During that time,

47
00:04:10,060 --> 00:04:12,420
I noticed Yunshen
treated her differently.

48
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:14,660
Zhizhi.

49
00:04:14,780 --> 00:04:16,620
I wanted to tell you about this.

50
00:04:17,020 --> 00:04:18,940
But I didn't know how to say this.

51
00:04:19,180 --> 00:04:22,340
Besides, Fu Yushen got in an accident
not long after he returned.

52
00:04:22,500 --> 00:04:24,420
I thought things ended between them.

53
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,380
It's fine, Ruanruan.

54
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:28,500
I don't blame you.

55
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:35,420
Ruanruan.

56
00:04:41,620 --> 00:04:42,660
I want to give up.

57
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:45,700
You want to give up Fu Yunshen?

58
00:04:47,500 --> 00:04:48,580
I used to think

59
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:50,780
that as long as I tried harder

60
00:04:51,340 --> 00:04:52,340
and became braver,

61
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,380
things would be different.

62
00:04:56,700 --> 00:04:57,380
But Ruanruan...

63
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:00,460
I realized

64
00:05:01,220 --> 00:05:04,100
nothing had changed.

65
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:06,420
But it has been years.

66
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:07,380
You even gave up music

67
00:05:07,420 --> 00:05:09,580
and switched to medicine
because of Fu Yunshen.

68
00:05:09,860 --> 00:05:11,020
Are you willing to let go?

69
00:05:12,220 --> 00:05:13,420
I don't regret going into medicine.

70
00:05:15,980 --> 00:05:16,940
To be honest,

71
00:05:18,300 --> 00:05:19,420
I'm not willing to let go

72
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:21,580
and I can't stand doing so.

73
00:05:23,540 --> 00:05:24,380
But, Ruanruan,

74
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:26,860
I'm scared.

75
00:05:28,700 --> 00:05:30,380
If I keep this up, I'm scared

76
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:32,500
that I'll become

77
00:05:33,900 --> 00:05:35,980
someone I detest.

78
00:05:41,300 --> 00:05:41,900
Zhizhi.

79
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:43,620
You're great.

80
00:05:44,100 --> 00:05:45,140
Very great.

81
00:05:45,380 --> 00:05:46,540
You're the best in the world.

82
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:48,700
No matter what decision you make,

83
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:50,340
I'll stand by you.

84
00:06:09,820 --> 00:06:10,860
(Upward a bit.)

85
00:06:12,180 --> 00:06:13,980
Left side. It's tilted.

86
00:06:15,900 --> 00:06:16,860
Almost there.

87
00:06:20,060 --> 00:06:20,500
Is this okay?

88
00:06:20,540 --> 00:06:21,860
Grandpa.

89
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:24,900
Is my calligraphy nice?

90
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:26,580
Pretty good.

91
00:06:27,300 --> 00:06:29,220
- I can write some more for you.
- Sure.

92
00:06:30,940 --> 00:06:31,660
Not bad.

93
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:33,980
Not bad.

94
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,100
What about this?

95
00:06:38,700 --> 00:06:39,580
- Paste it here.
- This one...

96
00:06:40,100 --> 00:06:41,220
Can I paste it here, Grandpa?

97
00:06:41,260 --> 00:06:42,660
Sure. Right here.

98
00:06:44,180 --> 00:06:45,220
Fu Yunshen!

99
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,060
Hurry up!

100
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,540
My arm feels sore!

101
00:06:47,660 --> 00:06:49,500
Okay.

102
00:06:50,460 --> 00:06:51,140
Hurry up!

103
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:52,100
Coming.

104
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:54,020
My wheelchair is a bit slow today.

105
00:06:56,940 --> 00:06:57,820
Here you go.

106
00:06:59,820 --> 00:07:00,700
Is this okay?

107
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:04,620
"Great fortune and prosperity."

108
00:07:10,380 --> 00:07:11,180
Very good.

109
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:13,580
Okay.

110
00:07:14,420 --> 00:07:15,020
Careful.

111
00:07:18,860 --> 00:07:20,020
How about this door?

112
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,580
You're exploiting me.

113
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:23,900
I need a rest now.

114
00:07:26,580 --> 00:07:29,420
Today is the first time
we celebrate Chinese New Year together.

115
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:30,340
Yes.

116
00:07:31,780 --> 00:07:32,980
Are you thinking of your granny?

117
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:36,020
You can tell that?

118
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:39,300
I do miss Granny.

119
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:41,660
In previous years,

120
00:07:41,860 --> 00:07:42,940
I used to fly back for Chinese New Year.

121
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:45,220
Because I didn't want her to be alone.

122
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:48,180
But don't worry.

123
00:07:48,500 --> 00:07:49,980
I gave her a call just now.

124
00:07:50,380 --> 00:07:52,180
Her voice told me she was happy.

125
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:54,860
Perhaps she pretended like that
to not worry me.

126
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:56,660
She told me she'd celebrate
with her friends.

127
00:07:57,460 --> 00:07:58,380
That's good.

128
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:03,060
How's your grandpa?

129
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:04,500
Is he in pink health?

130
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:07,100
Grandpa is doing pretty well.

131
00:08:08,980 --> 00:08:11,260
My brother and Ruanruan are with him.

132
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:13,980
My mother takes care of him too.

133
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:15,740
He won't be alone.

134
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:22,860
You haven't talked
in a long while, right?

135
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,500
I don't know

136
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,300
how to face Grandpa.

137
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:38,180
I don't want to upset him.

138
00:08:40,940 --> 00:08:42,740
But I can't bring myself

139
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:45,660
to comfort him either.

140
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,380
Anyway, Linda

141
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:51,700
will report my situation to them
at any time they want.

142
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:52,860
True.

143
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:58,900
But I think your grandpa
must have missed you very much.

144
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:01,340
Perhaps your voice

145
00:09:02,060 --> 00:09:03,580
is enough to soothe him.

146
00:09:12,380 --> 00:09:13,260
I go and get the door.

147
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:14,420
I'll put up the couplet later.

148
00:09:14,580 --> 00:09:15,260
Stay here and be good.

149
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:30,780
Coming.

150
00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:31,700
It's hot.

151
00:09:31,740 --> 00:09:34,060
You wouldn't enjoy such delicious food
without me.

152
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:37,020
It's hot, right?

153
00:09:37,420 --> 00:09:38,060
Yeah.

154
00:09:38,180 --> 00:09:39,020
Let me blow on your hand.

155
00:09:46,780 --> 00:09:48,700
Show some respect to the third wheel,

156
00:09:48,780 --> 00:09:49,620
will you?

157
00:10:00,660 --> 00:10:01,380
Mint.

158
00:10:01,820 --> 00:10:03,940
This is glutinous sesame, isn't it?

159
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:07,380
Practice your cooking skills, please.

160
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:09,980
Yunshen.

161
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:10,900
Eat this.

162
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:12,540
No.

163
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:15,820
I prefer glutinous tangyuans
that are cooked longer.

164
00:10:15,980 --> 00:10:17,020
I don't do much exercise,

165
00:10:17,100 --> 00:10:17,980
so they help with digestion.

166
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:23,420
This one is intact.

167
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:25,620
This one. This is good too.

168
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:29,180
You eat first.

169
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:29,820
Eat this.

170
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:31,940
I can't eat this anymore.

171
00:10:32,060 --> 00:10:33,300
Why did I even come here for?

172
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,020
It's Chinese New Year,
not Valentine's Day.

173
00:10:36,300 --> 00:10:36,700
Let's go.

174
00:10:37,140 --> 00:10:37,860
Wutong, let's go.

175
00:10:37,940 --> 00:10:38,620
Let's leave.

176
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:41,020
Stop talking when you're eating.

177
00:10:44,460 --> 00:10:45,220
Be gentle.

178
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:47,180
The dishes are in place.

179
00:10:47,300 --> 00:10:48,140
Put the fish in the center.

180
00:10:48,460 --> 00:10:49,380
We'll have more than a surplus every year.
[*"Surplus" and "fish" are homophones.]

181
00:10:50,660 --> 00:10:51,860
Dinner is ready?

182
00:10:51,860 --> 00:10:52,660
Yes.

183
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,540
Where's Grandpa?

184
00:10:56,660 --> 00:10:57,300
What's wrong with him?

185
00:10:57,420 --> 00:10:58,620
He was happy just now.

186
00:10:59,020 --> 00:11:00,260
He misses Yunshen.

187
00:11:00,780 --> 00:11:02,100
Go and talk to him.

188
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,540
Grandpa.

189
00:11:08,300 --> 00:11:10,220
Why the long face on this festive day?

190
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:12,220
Call Yunshen if you miss him.

191
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:14,100
Call him?

192
00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:15,100
He hung up on me

193
00:11:15,220 --> 00:11:16,180
and screened my calls.

194
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:18,940
It's embarrassing if I call him again.

195
00:11:19,340 --> 00:11:20,220
- Oh, my.
- Dad.

196
00:11:22,340 --> 00:11:22,900
Well...

197
00:11:23,100 --> 00:11:25,460
You're the closest to Yunshen,
aren't you?

198
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,140
He doesn't contact us

199
00:11:27,260 --> 00:11:28,580
probably because he doesn't want
to worry us

200
00:11:28,620 --> 00:11:29,980
with his vulnerable side.

201
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:32,580
Still, he should give me a call
on New Year's Eve.

202
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:34,780
If I drop dead,

203
00:11:35,060 --> 00:11:36,380
he'll regret this for sure.

204
00:11:36,780 --> 00:11:37,140
Dad.

205
00:11:37,220 --> 00:11:37,780
Don't say that.

206
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:38,420
Touch wood.

207
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:39,420
I'll call him.

208
00:11:39,820 --> 00:11:41,100
No, don't call him.

209
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:42,300
Jeez.

210
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,060
It's ringing.

211
00:11:55,460 --> 00:11:56,140
He didn't answer the call.

212
00:11:56,260 --> 00:11:57,180
See, I told you so.

213
00:11:57,260 --> 00:11:58,220
I knew it.

214
00:11:58,780 --> 00:11:59,660
Well, Dad. Come on.

215
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:00,580
Let's have the reunion dinner.

216
00:12:00,660 --> 00:12:01,700
No, I don't want to eat.

217
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:02,580
Let's go.

218
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:03,340
You enjoy yourself.

219
00:12:04,140 --> 00:12:04,660
Grandpa.

220
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:06,100
It's Yunshen.

221
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:08,660
Give it to me.

222
00:12:11,300 --> 00:12:12,180
Yunshen.

223
00:12:12,620 --> 00:12:13,420
How are you doing?

224
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:14,580
Are you faring well?

225
00:12:15,100 --> 00:12:16,260
I've missed you so much.

226
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:17,500
You look skinnier.

227
00:12:17,940 --> 00:12:18,740
- What has happened?
- I want to talk to him.

228
00:12:19,820 --> 00:12:20,540
Leave me alone.

229
00:12:22,660 --> 00:12:25,020
You're in good spirits.

230
00:12:25,620 --> 00:12:26,740
Have you gotten used to life over there?

231
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,420
Yes, Grandpa.

232
00:12:30,300 --> 00:12:31,220
Don't worry.

233
00:12:31,540 --> 00:12:32,580
How's your health?

234
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:33,420
Are you doing well?

235
00:12:34,220 --> 00:12:34,860
Not well.

236
00:12:35,620 --> 00:12:36,740
I can't eat or sleep.

237
00:12:36,940 --> 00:12:37,780
Fu Yunshen.

238
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:39,500
Grandpa misses you so much
that he's throwing a tantrum

239
00:12:39,540 --> 00:12:40,540
and refuses to eat dinner.

240
00:12:40,620 --> 00:12:41,340
Apologize to him now.

241
00:12:41,540 --> 00:12:44,140
How come my young and handsome grandpa

242
00:12:44,460 --> 00:12:46,380
has become grumpy?

243
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,140
Grandpa.

244
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:51,300
How about I give you a surprise?

245
00:12:51,500 --> 00:12:51,900
Well.

246
00:12:52,220 --> 00:12:53,580
Let me introduce

247
00:12:53,660 --> 00:12:55,900
your future granddaughter-in-law to you.

248
00:12:58,420 --> 00:12:59,580
She's Zhu Jiu, my girlfriend.

249
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:01,260
Nice to meet you, Grandpa.

250
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:02,420
Mrs. Fu.

251
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:03,420
Ruanruan.

252
00:13:05,100 --> 00:13:06,140
Hello, Miss Zhu.

253
00:13:06,500 --> 00:13:07,140
Please enjoy your chat.

254
00:13:08,340 --> 00:13:08,940
Yunshen.

255
00:13:09,100 --> 00:13:10,100
What's going on now?

256
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:11,860
This is a big decision
and yet you didn't discuss it with us.

257
00:13:12,020 --> 00:13:12,860
You're insensible.

258
00:13:12,980 --> 00:13:14,140
No, I'll talk to him about this.

259
00:13:14,300 --> 00:13:14,660
No, Dad.

260
00:13:14,780 --> 00:13:15,540
I'll do this.

261
00:13:15,660 --> 00:13:17,180
You go and prepare for the dinner.

262
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:17,860
Enough.

263
00:13:17,940 --> 00:13:18,620
Let's go, Madam Jiang.

264
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:19,420
Enough.

265
00:13:27,020 --> 00:13:27,620
Ruanruan.

266
00:13:28,420 --> 00:13:30,260
Do you know anything
about Yunshen's girlfriend?

267
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:31,780
No.

268
00:13:32,620 --> 00:13:33,780
Calm down.

269
00:13:33,940 --> 00:13:35,700
You can ask him
after Grandpa finishes the call.

270
00:13:36,700 --> 00:13:37,820
I'll give her a hand.

271
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:43,660
Yunshen.

272
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,820
Dating with a woman is something big.

273
00:13:46,100 --> 00:13:46,980
Don't worry, Grandpa.

274
00:13:47,580 --> 00:13:48,860
I'm faring well here. Look at me.

275
00:13:49,660 --> 00:13:51,660
Where's Xizhou?

276
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:54,060
He went to the restroom.

277
00:13:54,260 --> 00:13:55,220
I'll go and get him.

278
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:56,620
No, Grandpa.

279
00:13:56,700 --> 00:13:57,540
Let's talk first.

280
00:13:58,020 --> 00:13:59,020
Sure.

281
00:14:00,500 --> 00:14:01,660
How's the weather over there?

282
00:14:01,860 --> 00:14:02,660
Pretty good.

283
00:14:03,140 --> 00:14:03,700
Really?

284
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:05,100
How about the weather in Shanghai?

285
00:14:05,660 --> 00:14:06,740
It's good too.

286
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:08,100
Not bad.

287
00:14:08,300 --> 00:14:09,380
Grandpa, you must take care
of your health.

288
00:14:09,460 --> 00:14:10,020
I will.

289
00:14:10,460 --> 00:14:11,380
Turn your face to me.

290
00:14:11,580 --> 00:14:12,220
What do you want to do?

291
00:14:12,500 --> 00:14:13,340
Come here.

292
00:14:18,700 --> 00:14:19,900
How cute!

293
00:14:20,060 --> 00:14:21,380
How beautiful!

294
00:14:21,900 --> 00:14:22,660
Are you sure?

295
00:14:24,140 --> 00:14:24,860
Let me see.

296
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:27,740
In that case,

297
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:29,180
we must

298
00:14:29,620 --> 00:14:31,580
have a daughter in the future.

299
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:32,980
So that

300
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:34,940
she can rescue her dad

301
00:14:35,020 --> 00:14:37,460
from her mum's bullying.

302
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:40,420
You're so picky.

303
00:14:40,580 --> 00:14:41,620
Take it off if you don't like it.

304
00:14:42,380 --> 00:14:43,180
No, it's not that.

305
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:44,140
Can you not fantasize about things

306
00:14:44,220 --> 00:14:45,860
all the time?

307
00:14:50,460 --> 00:14:51,020
Zhu Jiu.

308
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:53,420
Once I recover,

309
00:14:53,700 --> 00:14:55,180
I'll take you out for a date.

310
00:14:55,740 --> 00:14:57,060
We'll dine in a restaurant,

311
00:14:57,340 --> 00:14:58,140
watch a movie,

312
00:14:58,460 --> 00:14:59,300
and go hiking.

313
00:15:00,460 --> 00:15:02,900
Unlike now,

314
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,380
staying at home with me.

315
00:15:07,460 --> 00:15:08,660
Leo told me

316
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:12,420
that international students like you
care much about Chinese New Year.

317
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:16,220
Do you want to join them
for the gathering?

318
00:15:17,020 --> 00:15:18,340
Of course, I don't want to.

319
00:15:18,580 --> 00:15:19,740
I want to stay here with you.

320
00:15:19,900 --> 00:15:21,300
I don't like noisy gatherings.

321
00:15:27,980 --> 00:15:29,100
When I was little,

322
00:15:29,220 --> 00:15:31,260
Granny used to buy me fireworks
during Chinese New Year.

323
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:33,180
Did you know

324
00:15:33,260 --> 00:15:34,380
sparklers?

325
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:35,140
Have you played those before?

326
00:15:36,820 --> 00:15:37,380
No.

327
00:15:37,740 --> 00:15:40,300
Grandpa only bought me huge fireworks.

328
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:43,660
Fu Yunshen. You're showing off, huh?

329
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:45,660
I was kidding.

330
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:47,900
When I was little,

331
00:15:48,020 --> 00:15:49,460
I always played with my brother.

332
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:51,260
But I was naughty,

333
00:15:51,620 --> 00:15:52,580
and I scared him a lot.

334
00:15:54,820 --> 00:15:56,460
I envy you so much.

335
00:15:57,020 --> 00:15:58,540
You have a big brother.

336
00:15:59,140 --> 00:16:01,980
I used to be alone back then.

337
00:16:04,220 --> 00:16:04,820
Zhu Jiu.

338
00:16:06,620 --> 00:16:07,700
Close your eyes.

339
00:16:09,220 --> 00:16:09,740
Why?

340
00:16:09,820 --> 00:16:10,300
Close your eyes.

341
00:16:13,580 --> 00:16:14,740
I want to perform a magic trick for you.

342
00:16:15,740 --> 00:16:16,180
All right.

343
00:16:16,500 --> 00:16:17,620
I'll trust you once.

344
00:16:23,260 --> 00:16:24,740
Don't fool me.

345
00:16:24,900 --> 00:16:26,700
No, I won't. Close your eyes tight.

346
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,620
When did you learn the magic trick?

347
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,420
When did you buy this?

348
00:16:43,060 --> 00:16:44,980
I really wanted this when I was little.

349
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:47,980
One more.

350
00:16:48,100 --> 00:16:48,620
Okay.

351
00:16:51,220 --> 00:16:53,380
- Can I have two?
- Here you go.

352
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:02,100
You should light up one for yourself.

353
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:02,820
Okay.

354
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:09,060
I didn't know you were a romantic guy.

355
00:17:13,380 --> 00:17:13,900
Yunshen.

356
00:17:14,700 --> 00:17:17,420
Did you know your wish will be answered

357
00:17:17,540 --> 00:17:18,540
if you make a wish upon a sparkler?

358
00:17:20,020 --> 00:17:21,580
Your wish will come true quicker

359
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:24,340
if you wish upon me.

360
00:17:25,940 --> 00:17:26,380
Fine.

361
00:17:26,740 --> 00:17:28,460
If so, I'll make a wish
upon the sparkler

362
00:17:28,580 --> 00:17:30,340
and you.

363
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:33,940
I hope Yunshen can stay safe

364
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,340
and healthy forever.

365
00:17:38,100 --> 00:17:38,900
All right.

366
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:43,020
From this year on, I'll stay up all night
on Chinese New Year's Eve

367
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:44,780
and New Year countdown with you.

368
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:47,180
We'll celebrate in our twenties,

369
00:17:47,300 --> 00:17:48,100
thirties,

370
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:49,020
forties,

371
00:17:49,180 --> 00:17:49,580
fifties,

372
00:17:49,700 --> 00:17:51,660
sixties, seventies, eighties,
and nineties

373
00:17:51,740 --> 00:17:52,460
together.

374
00:17:54,620 --> 00:17:55,100
We will.

375
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:01,820
Pinky, pinky bow-bell.

376
00:18:01,940 --> 00:18:04,100
Whoever tells a lie will sink down
into a bad place

377
00:18:04,180 --> 00:18:04,780
and never rise up again.

378
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:07,300
I promise.

379
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:09,300
I won't break it.

380
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:12,980
♪With vulnerability overwhelming you♪

381
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:15,420
♪Biting your lips
and facing away from me♪

382
00:18:15,820 --> 00:18:18,300
♪You break the walls of stubbornness♪

383
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:23,460
♪Once more, another sundown
swiftly passes by♪

384
00:18:23,780 --> 00:18:26,580
♪Love is like a lie at the end
of the century♪

385
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:27,340
Six.

386
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,180
Five.

387
00:18:30,100 --> 00:18:31,020
Four.

388
00:18:31,900 --> 00:18:32,700
Three.

389
00:18:33,700 --> 00:18:34,500
Two.

390
00:18:35,820 --> 00:18:36,340
One.

391
00:18:44,500 --> 00:18:49,140
♪A kiss can heal this wrecked world♪

392
00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:50,140
Happy Chinese New Year,

393
00:18:50,620 --> 00:18:51,300
Zhu Jiu.

394
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:53,740
Happy Chinese New Year,

395
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,100
Yunshen.

396
00:18:55,100 --> 00:18:58,460
♪If there is a slight possibility
of avoiding loneliness♪

397
00:18:58,540 --> 00:19:04,900
♪Let me endure the heavy rainfall
with you♪

398
00:19:05,100 --> 00:19:08,580
♪If there is a slight possibility♪

399
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:15,460
♪The moon that once shone for me
should stay radiate♪

400
00:19:15,540 --> 00:19:20,940
♪You'll regain happiness
when you are true to yourself♪

401
00:19:47,780 --> 00:19:49,060
Do you have something to tell me?

402
00:19:49,860 --> 00:19:51,580
How do you know that?

403
00:19:52,980 --> 00:19:53,500
What's it about?

404
00:19:54,700 --> 00:19:56,500
Will you work overtime today?

405
00:19:56,820 --> 00:19:58,580
Let's go on a date.

406
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:01,660
You see,

407
00:20:02,340 --> 00:20:04,380
I've been working late hours
at the gallery

408
00:20:04,780 --> 00:20:06,140
before Chinese New Year,

409
00:20:06,260 --> 00:20:07,860
and you've been on business trips.

410
00:20:08,940 --> 00:20:10,580
While we had a break,

411
00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:12,300
we had to return

412
00:20:12,420 --> 00:20:13,820
to our parents' home.

413
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:17,100
It's been a long while
since we spent time alone.

414
00:20:30,980 --> 00:20:33,540
You're married with a wife,

415
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,380
don't you feel pathetic

416
00:20:37,260 --> 00:20:39,060
for working all day long?

417
00:20:42,540 --> 00:20:42,940
Here.

418
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:48,100
After hearing what you said,

419
00:20:49,220 --> 00:20:50,180
I do find myself pretty pathetic.

420
00:20:51,700 --> 00:20:53,580
Let's go on a date today.

421
00:20:54,020 --> 00:20:56,300
I want to check out wedding gowns.

422
00:20:59,540 --> 00:20:59,940
All right.

423
00:21:00,100 --> 00:21:00,780
Really?

424
00:21:00,900 --> 00:21:02,460
I'll go and get changed now.

425
00:21:15,540 --> 00:21:17,620
Shift my schedule to the nighttime.

426
00:22:10,860 --> 00:22:11,700
You're awake.

427
00:22:14,500 --> 00:22:15,100
How do you feel now?

428
00:22:15,820 --> 00:22:16,500
Does it hurt?

429
00:22:18,420 --> 00:22:19,140
I'm skinnier.

430
00:22:22,820 --> 00:22:24,340
You won't lose weight in just one day.

431
00:22:25,300 --> 00:22:26,700
Maybe two days?

432
00:22:30,460 --> 00:22:31,500
Do your legs feel anything?

433
00:22:37,620 --> 00:22:38,260
No.

434
00:22:45,060 --> 00:22:45,780
How about this?

435
00:22:49,380 --> 00:22:50,260
No.

436
00:22:51,180 --> 00:22:52,060
It shouldn't be.

437
00:22:52,140 --> 00:22:53,900
You should've felt something
right after the operation.

438
00:22:59,220 --> 00:22:59,900
Ouch!

439
00:23:00,500 --> 00:23:01,380
I'm sorry.

440
00:23:02,020 --> 00:23:02,500
That hurts.

441
00:23:03,580 --> 00:23:05,060
Fu Yunshen, you liar!

442
00:23:05,580 --> 00:23:06,220
Dr. Zhu.

443
00:23:06,260 --> 00:23:06,700
I'm a patient.

444
00:23:06,740 --> 00:23:08,140
I need care.

445
00:23:16,020 --> 00:23:16,860
Congratulations.

446
00:23:17,140 --> 00:23:18,740
Finally, you can feel pain.

447
00:24:03,700 --> 00:24:04,380
Is this nice?

448
00:24:14,340 --> 00:24:14,900
Nice.

449
00:24:18,740 --> 00:24:19,660
Hello, James.

450
00:24:24,460 --> 00:24:25,940
How's your analysis result

451
00:24:25,980 --> 00:24:26,940
of the Singaporean company?

452
00:24:27,020 --> 00:24:28,140
I'll try on the next one.

453
00:24:28,220 --> 00:24:28,740
Sure.

454
00:24:36,220 --> 00:24:36,740
Okay.

455
00:24:57,300 --> 00:24:58,660
Make this quick.

456
00:24:59,860 --> 00:25:00,500
Xizhou.

457
00:25:02,580 --> 00:25:03,620
How about this one?

458
00:25:06,020 --> 00:25:06,700
Very good.

459
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:10,140
Regarding this,

460
00:25:10,980 --> 00:25:13,020
figure out the content in the contract
as soon as possible.

461
00:25:15,020 --> 00:25:15,500
Fine.

462
00:25:15,700 --> 00:25:17,460
Gather all the information.

463
00:25:29,220 --> 00:25:29,780
Not bad.

464
00:25:29,900 --> 00:25:30,460
Pretty good.

465
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:31,620
Okay.

466
00:25:32,980 --> 00:25:33,580
I'll hang up.

467
00:25:37,100 --> 00:25:38,540
"No problem", "pretty good", and "nice".

468
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:39,740
Don't they mean the same thing?

469
00:25:39,860 --> 00:25:41,260
I've tried on so many gowns.

470
00:25:41,460 --> 00:25:43,500
You can decide on your favorite one.

471
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:46,140
If not, buy them all.

472
00:25:48,940 --> 00:25:50,020
I need to take this.

473
00:25:53,380 --> 00:25:54,220
Hello, go on.

474
00:25:54,700 --> 00:25:56,420
Luo Jiang signed the contract
with Singapore on his own accord.

475
00:25:56,660 --> 00:25:58,580
The terms are the ones
you rejected before.

476
00:25:59,100 --> 00:25:59,900
Where's he now?

477
00:26:00,580 --> 00:26:01,380
At the office.

478
00:26:02,380 --> 00:26:03,340
Hold the contract.

479
00:26:03,460 --> 00:26:04,180
Okay.

480
00:26:04,300 --> 00:26:06,380
Book me a flight
to Singapore immediately.

481
00:26:06,980 --> 00:26:07,500
Right away.

482
00:26:07,620 --> 00:26:08,580
Okay, don't worry.

483
00:26:14,940 --> 00:26:15,540
Ruanruan?

484
00:26:29,220 --> 00:26:29,860
Excuse me.

485
00:26:30,460 --> 00:26:30,940
Yes?

486
00:26:31,740 --> 00:26:32,620
Where's my wife?

487
00:26:33,620 --> 00:26:34,980
She said she didn't want to disturb you,

488
00:26:35,100 --> 00:26:36,060
so she left first.

489
00:26:38,060 --> 00:26:38,580
Thank you.

490
00:26:39,060 --> 00:26:39,660
You're welcome.

491
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:54,940
This is infuriating!

492
00:26:57,700 --> 00:27:01,300
Did you really leave Xizhou
at the bridal boutique

493
00:27:01,420 --> 00:27:02,180
and ran away?

494
00:27:02,700 --> 00:27:03,340
I did.

495
00:27:06,380 --> 00:27:08,180
Very good, Gu Ruanruan.

496
00:27:08,660 --> 00:27:09,900
Well done!

497
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:11,940
Which side do you take?

498
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:13,980
Why are you so happy
when he walks over me?

499
00:27:15,980 --> 00:27:17,180
I really think

500
00:27:17,580 --> 00:27:19,260
you've done well on this.

501
00:27:20,660 --> 00:27:21,220
But,

502
00:27:21,540 --> 00:27:23,580
didn't you decide
on the wedding gown before?

503
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:24,780
Why are you choosing it again?

504
00:27:25,460 --> 00:27:26,740
Yes, I did.

505
00:27:26,860 --> 00:27:27,780
But I saw more beautiful ones

506
00:27:27,820 --> 00:27:29,380
when I went shopping.

507
00:27:30,700 --> 00:27:33,100
What I care isn't about the gown.

508
00:27:33,500 --> 00:27:35,780
I just want him
to spend more time with me.

509
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:37,940
Marriage is about two people.

510
00:27:38,020 --> 00:27:38,900
I hope we are involved

511
00:27:38,980 --> 00:27:40,700
in every step.

512
00:27:41,700 --> 00:27:42,460
Look at him now.

513
00:27:42,540 --> 00:27:43,980
He's been talking on the phone
all the while.

514
00:27:44,180 --> 00:27:45,420
Why should I be his wife?

515
00:27:45,540 --> 00:27:46,900
I want to be his phone

516
00:27:47,100 --> 00:27:48,940
so he can talk to me every day.

517
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,340
Zhou Zhizhi.

518
00:27:51,420 --> 00:27:53,020
Stop laughing, or I'll break you off.

519
00:27:53,780 --> 00:27:54,940
Well, I won't laugh.

520
00:27:58,460 --> 00:27:59,060
Ruanruan.

521
00:27:59,900 --> 00:28:01,620
If you want Xizhou to accompany you,

522
00:28:01,780 --> 00:28:02,980
don't go shopping.

523
00:28:03,580 --> 00:28:06,220
Men don't really enjoy shopping,

524
00:28:06,900 --> 00:28:08,180
especially during wedding photography.

525
00:28:08,580 --> 00:28:09,420
They feel

526
00:28:09,580 --> 00:28:10,860
that they're just a prop.

527
00:28:11,340 --> 00:28:13,780
Xizhou is a man with a rigid mind.

528
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,060
He really cares about you

529
00:28:16,340 --> 00:28:18,060
when he goes shopping with you.

530
00:28:18,460 --> 00:28:19,700
It's not a pleasant experience.

531
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:25,100
Maybe he thought you liked all the gowns,
that's why you couldn't decide.

532
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:27,100
So he told you to buy them all.

533
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:28,340
Well,

534
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:30,380
you should tell him what you mean.

535
00:28:30,540 --> 00:28:31,300
That's the right way to do it.

536
00:28:32,780 --> 00:28:33,740
Really?

537
00:28:34,820 --> 00:28:35,660
Of course.

538
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:40,830
[Xizhou]

539
00:28:41,660 --> 00:28:42,340
Pick it up.

540
00:28:42,660 --> 00:28:43,340
I think

541
00:28:43,500 --> 00:28:45,100
he's already learned his mistake.

542
00:28:51,700 --> 00:28:52,820
Ruanruan, where are you?

543
00:28:55,420 --> 00:28:56,060
Zhizhi's place.

544
00:28:58,620 --> 00:29:00,620
Can you ask Zhizhi
to send you home later?

545
00:29:00,860 --> 00:29:01,820
I have something urgent now.

546
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:03,580
I need to fly to Singapore.

547
00:29:04,100 --> 00:29:05,100
I'll accompany you next week.

548
00:29:05,620 --> 00:29:06,580
Let's do anything you like.

549
00:29:13,060 --> 00:29:14,540
You said he'd learned his mistake?

550
00:29:45,620 --> 00:29:48,070
[This one suits you the best!]

551
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:51,300
Gave me a carrot after the stick?

552
00:29:51,740 --> 00:29:52,820
Like I care.

553
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:25,930
[Xizhou, don't drink so much alcohol.]

554
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:34,220
(I've been staying overseas for years,)

555
00:30:34,380 --> 00:30:36,340
I still find Chinese cuisine
to be the best.

556
00:30:36,860 --> 00:30:39,380
I can't get used to Western wine.

557
00:30:39,740 --> 00:30:40,460
Today,

558
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:42,260
let's have some drinks

559
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,300
to celebrate our collaboration.

560
00:30:46,300 --> 00:30:47,460
I'm sorry, Mr. He.

561
00:30:47,980 --> 00:30:49,420
But my stomach doesn't feel well today.

562
00:30:49,940 --> 00:30:52,540
We'll have a blast
when you come to Shanghai next time.

563
00:30:53,020 --> 00:30:53,980
You don't accept my offer

564
00:30:54,700 --> 00:30:56,140
or you don't want
a pleasant collaboration with me?

565
00:30:58,060 --> 00:30:59,140
How could that be?

566
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:01,460
I'm looking forward to
collaborating with you.

567
00:31:02,660 --> 00:31:06,180
That's why I flew all the way here
to discuss the contract with you.

568
00:31:06,580 --> 00:31:07,380
What contract?

569
00:31:07,860 --> 00:31:08,820
Didn't we just sign one lately?

570
00:31:09,700 --> 00:31:11,860
I'm not satisfied with that one.

571
00:31:12,940 --> 00:31:14,740
So, I bring you a new contract
this time.

572
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:19,260
[Drug Supply Contract]

573
00:31:29,580 --> 00:31:30,900
Are you kidding me?

574
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:35,260
