has been facing financial problems

580
00:31:56,220 --> 00:31:57,420
for several months, right?

581
00:31:58,020 --> 00:32:01,140
You requested to lower the cost
and extend payment terms

582
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:04,020
because you want to use Lingtian's order

583
00:32:04,140 --> 00:32:05,500
to relieve your financial problems.

584
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:07,780
