your problem from the root.

586
00:32:11,340 --> 00:32:12,620
What are you trying to get at?

587
00:32:27,860 --> 00:32:29,740
I'm having dinner
with Mr. He of Jinghui.

588
00:32:31,020 --> 00:32:32,220
He wants to have a word with you.

589
00:32:36,380 --> 00:32:37,740
It's James from Redstone Investments.

590
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:40,460
